SIMPLE: why-not
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Why-not
<hw>Why"-not`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A violent and
peremptory procedure without any assigned reason; a sudden conclusive
happening.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When the church⟦br⟧
Was taken with a <qex>why-not</qex> in the lurch.</q>
<rj><qau>Hudibras.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This game . . . was like to have been lost with a
<qex>why-not</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Nugae Antiq.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wicca</ent>⟦br⟧
